cp4d.readme
1. Download Kubeconfig and SSH Key
2. Rename vm_ssh_key.vm to cp4d_ssh_key.vm
3. Change permissions on cp4d_ssh_key.vm

	chmod 600 ~/Downloads/cp4d_ssh_key.vm

4. Copy conf_kubeconfig_download.conf to Bastion home directory as kubeconfig [Note: use Bastion SSH Connection info from Request]

example:

scp -P 10022 -o IdentitiesOnly=yes -i ~/Downloads/cp4d_ssh_key.vm ~/Downloads/conf_kubeconfig_download.conf itzuser@api.itz-e0lhw6.infra02-lb.dal12.techzone.ibm.com:~/kubeconfig

5. Copy cp4d*.yaml files to Bastion home directory

scp -P 10022 -o IdentitiesOnly=yes -i ~/Downloads/cp4d_ssh_key.vm ./cp4d-*.yml itzuser@api.itz-e0lhw6.infra02-lb.dal12.techzone.ibm.com:~/

6. Copy Scripts files to Bastion home directory

scp -P 10022 -o IdentitiesOnly=yes -i ~/Downloads/cp4d_ssh_key.vm ./*.sh itzuser@api.itz-e0lhw6.infra02-lb.dal12.techzone.ibm.com:~/


